{
  "id": "adv_group_tri_04_01",
  "title": "TRINITYAiLE 04 01",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さあ、NEXT VENUSグランプリ予選",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ the Next Venus Grand Prix preliminaries",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 4.524045376107097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "勝ち上がったのは……TRINITYAiLEだぁ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The winner is… TRINITYAiLE!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.524045376107097,
      "endTime": 9.963945960998537,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3642.6212905595694,
          "startTime": 8.166666666666666
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "しかも、圧倒的な差を付けての大勝利！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's more‚ it's a landslide victory!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.133333333333333,
      "endTime": 14.7717313721776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ではさっそく、今のお気持ちをお聞かせ下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ please tell us how you feel now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.7717313721776,
      "endTime": 18.196598466237386,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 18.396598466237386
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "素直に嬉しく思います\nこれも、私達を応援して下さったみなさん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm honestly happy.\nThis is also thanks to everyone who supported us…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.396598466237386,
      "endTime": 24.523945267995202,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 24.7239452679952
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "そして、一緒にステージに立ってくれた優とすみれ\n二人のおかげだと思います。ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And Yu and Sumire who stood on stage with us.\nI think it's thanks to the two of you. Thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.7239452679952,
      "endTime": 32.485986169179284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 32.68598616917928
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "でも、うちらの目標はもっと上ですから\nこれからもさらに気張っていきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But our goal is even higher.\nSo we'll keep pushing ourselves even harder.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.68598616917928,
      "endTime": 39.00111096700032,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 39.21931950251262
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな～！　次の最終予選も、応援よろしくね～！\n絶対、決勝のステージに連れて行ってあげるから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone! Please cheer us on in the next final qualifying round!\nI'll definitely take you to the final stage!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.21931950251262,
      "endTime": 48.085986169179264,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7199.999999999989,
          "startTime": 46.41931950251261
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 49.3859861691793
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 49.3859861691793
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "もう予選も次の一回でおしまい\nなんや、気づいたらあっという間やったなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The next preliminary round is the last one.\nIt feels like it's gone by so fast.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.55265283584593,
      "endTime": 57.52231292724608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 57.72231292724609
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "そうね\nそれも、順当に勝ち進んでいるおかげだと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right.\nI think it's because we've been winning steadily.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.72231292724609,
      "endTime": 61.91301589012145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 62.15564626057942
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワと当たらない限り苦戦はしない……\nっていう当初の想定通りではあるけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As long as we don't run into LizNoir‚ we won't have a hard time…\nWhich is as we initially assumed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.15564626057942,
      "endTime": 67.84546492894489,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 68.0454649289449
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "キレイにブロック分かれてるからなぁ\n案外、社長が裏で手を回してたりして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The blocks are neatly divided.\nMaybe the president pulled some strings behind the scenes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.0454649289449,
      "endTime": 74.3432881673177,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 74.53186736069618
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "……仮にそうだとしたら、ちょっと癪だけど\n相手がリズノワでも負けるつもりはないもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…If that were the case‚ I'd be a little annoyed‚\nBut I don't intend to lose‚ even if our opponent is LizNoir.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.53186736069618,
      "endTime": 80.43186726532875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 80.63186731301248
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、そんなことをするような人じゃない……とは思う\n純粋に、実力で測る人だと思うから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I don't think he's the kind of person to do that…\nI think he's someone who judges purely on merit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.63186731301248,
      "endTime": 88.86207122765481,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "せやなぁ\nとはいえ可能性はゼロじゃないし、案外、姫……あれ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true.\nBut it's not impossible‚ maybe Hime… Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.06666666666666,
      "endTime": 97.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 89.06997225905458
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 97.53847573424379
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "すみれ？　大丈夫？\nなんだか、ボーッとしていたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire? Are you okay?\nYou seemed kind of spaced out…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.53847573424379,
      "endTime": 102.1088385882477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "あ……ううん、ごめん！\nちょっと考え事してただけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… uh‚ sorry!\nI was just thinking about something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.30514240091043,
      "endTime": 106.71786336724955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 106.90543457232417
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、今日はこのまま瑠依ちゃん家にお泊まりして\n明日の朝の新幹線で山形に帰るでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You see‚ I'm staying at your place tonight‚ Rui-chan‚\nand I'm going back to Yamagata on the Shinkansen tomorrow morning‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.90543457232417,
      "endTime": 113.39051414690911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 113.60543457232414
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "それで、明日のスケジュールとか\nいろいろ整理してたの、頭の中で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I was just‚\norganizing things in my head.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.60543457232414,
      "endTime": 118.91330286227165,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 119.11330286227168
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "そっかぁ……やっぱ大変やな\nすみれちゃんも、こっち出て来れればいいのになぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… It must be tough.\nI wish Sumire-chan could come live here too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.11330286227168,
      "endTime": 126.71330305300654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 126.91330305300656
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "うん……やっぱり、そうだよね\nその方が……でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… That's true.\nThat would be… but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.91330305300656,
      "endTime": 132.94246383868162,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 133.1424638386817
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "とりあえず、私達ももう帰りましょうか\n長居してても休まらないもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ should we head back now?\nStaying any longer won't help us rest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.1424638386817,
      "endTime": 138.4362735386939,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6990.869494651633,
          "startTime": 140.13333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 139.37579717201504
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 139.475797172015
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "おじゃましま～す",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse us~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.9757971720151,
      "endTime": 142.6091305053484,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
